<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039123" n="1"/> 
  <opener><salute>Amico meo maxime colendo <abbr>M.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1012090132" type="person">Andre<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Ritzio</rs> Salutem et Officia.</salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Diu est et quidem nimis diu, quod nullas ad te dedi literas, amice optime, ita ut me supin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>negligenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> reum et reprehensione dignum judicandi justas te habere causas omnino crederem,
    <lb/>nisi te cognita tam diutini silentii causa ultro mihi condonaturum sperarem. Co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odam nempe
    <lb/>ad te scribendi occasionem mihi abstulit brevis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam in <rs key="place_GEO-2658822" type="place">Galliam</rs> peregrinatio, ab initio enim
    <lb/><date>mensis Februarii</date> <rs key="place_GEO-2661552" type="place">Bernam</rs> profectus ibique aliquandiu co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oratus inde me <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genevam</rs> contuli, qua
    <lb/>iterum <date>post mensem</date> fere relicta iter per <rs key="place_GEO-2751773" type="place">Lugdunum</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Lutetiam</rs> versus direxi; ex quo itinere jam
    <lb/><date>ante aliquot hebdomadas</date>, Deo sit gratia, feliciter redux <rs type="letter">responsionem</rs> ad <rs type="lostletter">literas</rs> tuas ultimas,
    <lb/>quas mihi apud exteros degenti <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Pater</rs> ante semestre circiter transmiserat, consulto usque ad <rs type="organisation">nun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dinas</rs> nostras distuli, ut possem illas una cum scripto, <del><gap/></del>quod petis, <abbr>Dni</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-12209025X" type="person">Werenfelsii</rs> <rs type="biblio">de Syncre<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tismo Lutheranorum et Reformatorum</rs> <abbr>Dnis</abbr> <rs key="pers_no_GND_id" type="person">Zublinis</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2658822" type="place">Sangallum</rs> perferend<del><gap/></del><add>a</add>s tradere, ubi de<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>inde eas tibi mittendi co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odam occasionem habebunt. Gradus Doctoratus mihi nondum, ut tu
    <lb/>quidem existimas, collatus est; forsan te decepit titulus <rs type="biblio">Dissertationis</rs> me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quamvis enim pro
    <lb/>Doctoratu disputaverim, animus tamen non est gradum tam cito capessere, etsi id primo
    <lb/>quoque die mihi facere liceret; Interim tibi nihilominus gratias ago pro gratulatione huma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nissima et sinceris, quibus me prosequeris, votis, Deumque vicissim precor, ut te omni bono
    <lb/>cumulatum Ecclesi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odo diu conservet. De eventu electionis <rs type="person">Pastorum</rs> nihil 
    <pb facs="1039124" n="2"/> 
    <lb/>scio, quod tibi scribere queam, nisi quod, Deo sit laus, omnia nunc tranquilla sint, et quod <abbr>Dno</abbr>
    <lb/>Diacono <rs key="pers_DE-588-104222069" type="person">Im Hof</rs> cum <rs type="person">uxore</rs> sua nunc melius quam ab initio conveniat. Maximum tamen infortuni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>um, quod <date>ante semestre</date> novo cuidam <rs type="person">Pastori</rs> accidit, te (nisi id aliunde jam cognoveris) celare non
    <lb/>possum: <date>Annus</date> circiter est, ex quo <abbr>Ampl.</abbr> noster Magistratus pago <foreign xml:lang="ger"><rs key="place_GEO-2660142" type="place"><choice><orig>klein</orig><reg>Klein</reg></choice> <choice><orig>hüningen</orig><reg>Hüningen</reg></choice></rs></foreign> <rs type="place">Urbi</rs> proximo
    <lb/>templum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dificare, propriumque habere <rs type="person">Pastorem</rs> indulsit, curamque gregis hujus unanimi voce
    <lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Jacobo Me<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>ero</rs>, co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>uni illi nostro <rs type="person">amico</rs> integerrimo, detulit, qui postquam munus suum paucis
    <lb/>post diebus aggressus fuit, <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Brandm<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>lleri</rs> Pastoris in <foreign xml:lang="ger"><rs key="place_GEO-2660656" type="place">Gelterkinden</rs></foreign> <rs type="person">filiam</rs> uxorem duxit; acci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dit autem ut, cum huncce <rs type="person">socerum</rs> suum <date>tertia post nuptias hebdomade</date> visitasset, discedens ab
    <lb/><rs type="person">uxoris</rs> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="person">fratre</rs>, quem <rs type="person">comitem</rs> habebat, ex improviso ictu sclopeti plumbo, quod ipse <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Me<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>erus</rs>
    <lb/>antea in minutias conciderat, onerati in imo ventre lethaliter vulneraretur; in <rs type="place">Urbem</rs> autem postea
    <lb/>delatus et <rs type="person">Medicis</rs> traditus tribus tantum diebus supervixit; mortem ejus multi doluere, meque
    <lb/>non parum afflixit de infelici ejus obitu nuntius; Successor ei datus est <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102039186" type="person">Fre<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice></rs> <foreign xml:lang="ger">am <rs type="place"><choice><orig>graben</orig><reg>Graben</reg></choice></rs></foreign>.</p>
<closer><lb/>Vale et ama Tuum <signed>NBernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>.</signed>
  <lb/><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1710-11-13">13. <abbr>Nov.</abbr> 1710</date>.</dateline></closer>
  <pb facs="1039125" n="3" type="empty"/>
</div>
